<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-670] Unions don&apos;t skip unrecognizable fields correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-670</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m getting a NullPointerException when trying to read a Union struct off the wire which has a value that&apos;s not recognized by the current version of the code. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
